# frontend-design-system

Source of truth: `docs/ux/landing-page-v1.md` and root `CLAUDE.md`'s Product Design Philosophy. Full review checklist (mirrors the Claude Code `frontend-reviewer` agent): `.claude/agents/frontend-reviewer.md`.

- Dark-only theme (`color-scheme: dark` is set in `globals.css` — don't remove it; native scrollbar/select/input controls depend on it).
- Use the existing tokens (`--gold`, `--hairline`, `--muted-foreground`) instead of ad-hoc colors.
- Gold accent is used sparingly (CTAs, "Active" status) — not as a general decoration color.
- Headings use Fraunces (`font-heading`); body is Geist Sans.
- Card lists must distinguish **Active** (MVP-supported: HDFC Infinia, HDFC Diners Black, Axis Atlas, Axis Magnus, Amex Platinum Travel, SBI Cashback) from **Coming soon** — never mark a non-MVP card Active.
- Should feel "intelligent, premium, strategic, trustworthy" — avoid cluttered dashboards, generic AI-chat patterns, or jargon-heavy copy.
